<i>noun</i>: 솜씨 [솜씨] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>솜씨 [솜씨]</dt><br>
<dd>1. skill; dexterity</dd><br>
<dd>손으로 무엇을 만들거나 다루는 재주.</dd><br>
<dd>A talent of handling or making something with hands.</dd><br>
<dd>2. skill; deftness; tact</dd><br>
<dd>일을 처리하는 수단이나 능력.</dd><br>
<dd>A tactic or an ability to cope with a certain work.</dd><br>
